### 4.3. Player interaction {#4.3.-player-interaction}

Players hit the start game, and then are shown a menu where they pick their class. From there the game begins and they can use cards in their hand, then draw, then their turn ends and the next player clicks start turn. There is a separation between the trunks so player 1 does not see what is in player 2’s hand. The cards have onHover and onClick functions that determines what happens

