Background texture  
Dice for thief dodge

## 5\. Graphics and audio {#5.-graphics-and-audio}

### 5.1. Visual system {#5.1.-visual-system}

Minimalistic design for the demo. Flat background and cards as well as a stack of cards that represent the deck

#### 5.1.1. Player camera {#5.1.1.-player-camera}

Camera switches between three points and also a start next turn screen that blocks the view for the next player

### 5.2. Interface {#5.2.-interface}

Minimal interface that counts the gold, mana, and shows your class abilities. Repair armor and use magic for knight and mage respectively.
